{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.200", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Politisch Verfolgte genie\u00dfen Asylrecht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.760", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein verb\u00fcrgtes Grundrecht unserer Verfassung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.761", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Seit den 1950er-Jahren hat die Bundesrepublik rund 5,5\u00a0Millionen Menschen aufgenommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.761", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.960", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die hierzulande Asyl begehrten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.200", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen stolz sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.000", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass so viele Menschen unser Land als einen Ort der Freiheit und Sicherheit sch\u00e4tzen und dass unsere Gesellschaft die Offenheit besa\u00df und besitzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.001", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihnen Schutz zu bieten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.001", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.002", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber diese Offenheit war nie voraussetzungslos. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.002", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.320", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Selbstverst\u00e4ndlich wurden Asylantr\u00e4ge immer auf ihre Berechtigung hin \u00fcberpr\u00fcft und h\u00e4ufig auch abschl\u00e4gig beschieden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.321", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den letzten Jahrzehnten haben wir immer wieder gesehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.321", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.322", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es L\u00e4nder gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.322", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.440", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aus denen besonders viele Menschen zu uns kamen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.280", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deren Antr\u00e4ge auf Asyl ganz offensichtlich unbegr\u00fcndet waren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Entwicklung ist auch Folge dessen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.000", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Deutschland nach wie vor kein Einwanderungsgesetz besitzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.960", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Menschen einen klaren und nachvollziehbaren Weg er\u00f6ffnen w\u00fcrde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.280", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nach Deutschland zu kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier zu arbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.400", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich ein neues Leben aufzubauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.600", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist und bleibt ein Vers\u00e4umnis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.880", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch zum Nachteil unseres Landes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.881", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wir in dieser Legislaturperiode endlich beheben m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.881", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Asylrecht war f\u00fcr viele Menschen ein Umweg, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.680", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber den sie Eintritt in unsere Gesellschaft zu finden hofften. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.681", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist menschlich verst\u00e4ndlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.681", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.682", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber politisch wie rechtlich ein unhaltbarer Zustand. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.682", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.683", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn das Asylrecht als Einwanderungsrecht genutzt wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.683", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.684", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann strapaziert das nicht nur unseren Rechtsstaat; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.684", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.480", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es belastet auch die Akzeptanz des Asylrechts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.840", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade wer die Offenheit unserer Gesellschaft erhalten will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.240", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der muss dieses Recht rechtsstaatlich handhaben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.720", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir stellen darum nicht das Recht auf Asyl infrage. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.721", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ganz im Gegenteil: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.721", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.960", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen es mit Blick auf diese L\u00e4nder so ausgestalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.800", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es handhabbar bleibt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.440", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn der Rechtsstaat muss seine Durchsetzungsf\u00e4higkeit beweisen und die Kontrolle behalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.720", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sehen doch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.000", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass heute nur ein Bruchteil der Asylbewerber aus den Maghreb-Staaten bei uns anerkannt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.001", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur 6,3\u00a0Prozent der Antragsteller aus Marokko, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.001", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.002", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "3,6\u00a0Prozent der Antragsteller aus Algerien und 2,8\u00a0Prozent der Antragsteller aus Tunesien haben zuletzt \u00fcberhaupt einen Aufenthaltsstatus bei uns bekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.002", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.003", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung hat deutlich nachgewiesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.003", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.004", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese L\u00e4nder strengen Anspr\u00fcchen gen\u00fcgen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.004", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.005", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Einsch\u00e4tzung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.005", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.006", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die \u00fcbrigens die Niederlande und \u00d6sterreich bereits beschlossen haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.006", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.200", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Blick nach Frankreich zeigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Vorschl\u00e4ge von Emmanuel Macron in eine \u00e4hnliche Richtung gehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.401", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es lohnt sich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.401", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.402", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier hinzuschauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.402", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.403", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir ein gemeinsames funktionierendes Asylrecht in Europa wollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.403", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.404", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch mit der Einstufung dieser L\u00e4nder als sichere Herkunftsstaaten gibt es weiterhin Offenheit unseres Landes f\u00fcr diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.404", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.405", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Opfer politischer Verfolgung sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.405", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.520", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch die Voraussetzung f\u00fcr ein ausf\u00fchrliches Anerkennungsverfahren sollte bei Antragstellern aus diesen L\u00e4ndern zumindest sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.800", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie glaubhafte Indizien f\u00fcr ihr Anliegen vorbringen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.840", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da gelten \u00fcbrigens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.680", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie bei dem Beschluss\u00a02015 zum Westbalkan, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.120", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Worte Winfried Kretschmanns: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.600", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Ma\u00dfnahmen zur Verfahrensbeschleunigung beinhalten auch Restriktionen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.960", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber sie stellen niemals das Asylrecht infrage."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.000", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wissen um verbleibende Unsicherheiten gerade f\u00fcr homosexuelle Menschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.120", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade deshalb gew\u00e4hrt unser Land auch weiterhin Menschen aus diesen Herkunftsstaaten Schutz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.360", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn ihnen ein individuelles Verfolgungsschicksal droht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.400", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichzeitig brauchen wir ein Einwanderungsgesetz und gegebenenfalls als \u00dcberbr\u00fcckung erleichterte Arbeitsvisa."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.040", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich hoffe auf eine l\u00f6sungsorientierte Debatte im Ausschuss; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.200", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn ich bin mir ganz sicher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.080", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die meisten hier im Saal unsere Anliegen teilen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Grundrecht auf Asyl gew\u00e4hrleisten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.280", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schnellere Verfahren und f\u00fcr die, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.281", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die berechtigterweise hierbleiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.281", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.282", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gute Integrationsbedingungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.282", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.283", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.283", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.000", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu einer Kurzintervention erteile ich dem Kollegen Sven Lehmann von der Fraktion B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}